      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東門之墠.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東門之墠，茹藘在阪。其室則邇，其人甚遠。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Near the level ground at the east gate,
Is the madder plant on the bank.
The house is near there,
But the in an is very far away.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
