      <prop type="x-translation-ref">東門之墠.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>東門之栗，有踐家室。豈不爾思？子不我即。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>By the chestnut trees at the east gate,
Is a row of houses.
Do I not think of you?
But you do not come to me.</seg>
      </tuv>
